t of the Constitution of Ireland|deleted in 1973]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.irishstatutebook.ie/1972/en/act/cam/0005/index.html|title=Fifth Amendment of the Constitution Act, 1972.|work=[[Irish Statute Book]]|accessdate=3 December 2014}}</ref>|group=note}} || [[Church of Ireland]] || [[Anglican]] || 1871
